WaterwayCity_House8_Text_Old_Man:
	.string "You see that temple just outside?\p"
	.string "That's the Colossus Temple.\p"
	.string "It's been there for centuries, long\n"
	.string "before Waterway City was even built.\p"
	.string "People say it was once a place where\n"
	.string "ancient Pokémon were worshipped…\l"
	.string "Maybe even by Pokémon themselves!$"

WaterwayCity_House8_Text_Old_Woman:
	.string "Living close to the Colossus Temple…\p"
	.string "Sometimes I can feel a strange energy\n"
	.string "in the air, especially at night.\p"
	.string "My Pokémon are always restless when we\n"
	.string "walk by.\p"
	.string "I've never been brave enough to\n"
	.string "explore it myself, though.\p"
	.string "They say only the most daring Trainers\n"
	.string "can unlock its secrets.$"
